            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>soy sauce</strong> and <strong>crème fraîche</strong> and cook for 30 secs, stirring frequently</p><p>Tip: Scrape any bits from the bottom of the pan as this will add extra flavour to the sauce!</p><p>Add the<strong> cracked black pepper </strong>and <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong> and<strong> </strong>cook for 1-2 min further or until the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>peppercorn sauce</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of boiled water if your sauce is looking a little thick!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
